  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn your <strong>MIDI keyboard</strong> into a <strong>computer keyboard</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use MIDI keyboard to type and play games just like using computer keyboard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or turn on [global monitor] to generate music when typing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your computer is connected to multiple MIDI devices, please select the correct MIDI port for listening. Double click the corresponding device in the [Settings] ->[Commonly used] ->[MIDI port] list to achieve monitoring. </p>",
